user_description: Working to improve health and care for Enfield as part of north central London clinical commissioning group (@NHS_NCLCCG). Monitored Mon - Fri, 9am - 5pm.
text:
You can get your #CovidVaccine at Carlton House Surgery’s Pfizer and AstraZeneca walk-in vaccination clinic. Open Mon - Sun, 9am - 6pm.

No booking needed. Everyone aged 18+ can get a jab. Second doses given 8 weeks after the 1st. https://t.co/Q5ATOH1ytr
